n Loose Women' after rows  We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1742, \"end\": 1754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denise_Welch\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Denise Welch\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denise_Welch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denise_Welch\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 2010, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2011, \"to\": 2043, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy    In other news during the Olympics, there were remarkable scenes when a sports event came to a standstill twice.\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2181, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's skiff medal race, featuring Team GB, was already underway when it was suddenly stopped by organisers.\", \"from\": 2182, \"to\": 2293, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2220, \"end\": 2227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999574242475026, \"rank\": 3.73917999003023e-05, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was because of a sudden and dramatic shift in the wind's direction.\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2367, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This meant a swift restart, but then organisers stopped the event again because of a lack of wind.\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2466, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The race is potentially rescheduled for Friday.BBCsailing commentator Niall Myant expressed his astonishment at the development, saying: \\\"I have never seen that in a medal race at the Olympic level.\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2666, \"